"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Nintendo: 21M \\n Playstation: 13.7M \\n Xbox: 8M \\n  \\n VR is happening ... now! \\n  \\n As Zuck reasons, bandwidth evolution leads to social experiences becoming more immersive \\n  \\n Text (Blogs/Orkut?) --> Insta (Images) --> Tiktok (Video) --> Fortnite (Interactive Video) --> VR (Immersive Video) \\n  \\n We do have older formats still relevant in niches, but the majority moves to the most immersive and seamless experience possible \\n  \\n FB almost missed the mobile boat, if it weren't for Instagram acquisition \\n  \\n This time they leapfrogged a couple of steps directly to VR with Oculus \\n  \\n FB acquired Oculus in 2014 ... almost 10-12 years before VR becomes mainstream \\n  \\n The level of insight required to make that call in 2014 is remarkable! \\n  \\n Even if web3 protocols win the metaverse short-term ... with a $10 Bil investment from FB, difficult to match the level of polish Zuck will bring to the table\",\"timestamp\":1642498960,\"title\":\"Oculus sold 8.1 million VR headsets in 2021\"},\"digest\":\"mPVmdHqyGO4TlOtJUWzYwntwAK_q2RDV016eeiWEmuw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF41DF18b77bec4e196Ecf0178820313F9Fca3562\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0egU7ASP7p-8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"sizrSE4_a0svcHBwjUqOlvZ6sJkmGk0hyqH6SvIW43giKdYhH5CYQNGCR8HWZ-j-Y7rFmkoqFkKgLdz4eGR1GQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xfca35987db28220465f949e8414d396e911f842c8caa46dbdad7fad0118798ab7d26b8f7967ca9be532786093ace73c092ed916e94d8da872148d1a00a92891c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0